window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>He's a blood stained monster, but one look at her and he knows she will be his.</p> <p>Gaven Belmonte is a cold-hearted killer. A hitman. Now, he's my jailer.</p> <p>Even though he's twice my age, I'm being forced into an arranged marriage to secure Gaven's position as the next head of the Price Family Syndicate.</p> <p>Marriage or war?</p> <p>Pain or Pleasure?</p> <p>Murder or love?</p> <p>It doesn't matter that Gaven makes me burn for him. I'm simply a means to an end, a pawn for him to gain everything he's ever wanted. Well, I wont let this be my end. I'll take back control.</p> <p>If he wants my hand in marriage, then hell have to fight me for it.</p> <p>Tropes: Arranged Marriage, Mafia Romance, Dark Romance, Age Gap Romance, BDSM.</p> <p>Trigger Warnings: Degradation, Sexual Bondage, Sexual violence, Murder/mention of murder etc.</p>"; 
